OL,7,FA former teacher and school principal
OL,8,Fconvicted of historical child sex
OL,9,Fabuse showed no remorse and no mercy
OL,10,Fto his victims, a judge has said.
OL,12,FCrown Court judge Patrick Lynch KC was
OL,13,Fresponding to a plea for leniency in
OL,14,Fthe sentencing of former Christian
OL,15,FBrother Paul Dunleavy, 89, with a
OL,16,Fdefence barrister saying there is very
OL,17,Freal prospect the defendant will die
OL,18,Fin jail.
