OL,4,Cshowed 'no mercy' to victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDunleavy, with an address in Glen
OL,8,FRoad, Belfast, was found guilty in
OL,9,FSeptember of 36 charges of historical
OL,10,Fsexual abuse against nine boys.
OL,12,FThe charges included indecent assault
OL,13,Fand gross indecency with or towards a
OL,14,Fchild.
OL,16,FThe offences were committed between
OL,17,F1964 and 1991 while Dunleavy worked at
OL,18,Ffour schools in Belfast, Newry and
OL,19,FArmagh. The victims were aged between
OL,20,Fseven and 14 at the time.
