OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDunleavy is already serving a prison
OL,8,Fsentence having been convicted
OL,9,Fpreviously on two separate occasions
OL,10,Fof sexual offences against children in
OL,11,Fhis care.
OL,13,FProsecuting barrister Neil Connor KC
OL,14,Ftold a sentencing hearing at Belfast
OL,15,FCrown Court on Friday that publicity
OL,16,Faround the previous convictions had
OL,17,Fled to further victims coming forward.
