OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe added: "This was a substantial,
OL,8,Fcomplicated investigation involving a
OL,9,Fnumber of victims... this (case) is
OL,10,Fthe largest in terms of the number of
OL,11,Fvictims. Nine in this case, 18 in
OL,12,Ftotal."
OL,14,FDefence barrister Gary McHugh KC said:
OL,15,F"The most obvious feature I would
OL,16,Finvite the court to have regard to is
OL,17,Fthe defendant's age.
