OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"Clearly this defendant is going to be
OL,8,Fin prison well into his mid to late
OL,9,F90s and the very real prospect is that
OL,10,Fthis defendant may die in prison.
OL,12,F"There may be those who say so be it,
OL,13,Fbut it is not as clear cut as the
OL,14,Fpunitive component of the sentencing
OL,15,Fexercise.
OL,17,F"Prison for somebody in his 90s will
OL,18,Fbe a significantly more difficult
OL,19,Fplace than somebody in their 30s or
OL,20,F40s."
