OL,7,FMr McHugh added: "With all that goes
OL,8,Fwith being a very elderly prisoner,
OL,9,Fthat sense of isolation which comes
OL,10,Fwith being so old compared to the rest
OL,11,Fof the prisoners, any sentence we say
OL,12,Fis more difficult for this defendant
OL,13,Fis more difficult than it would be for
OL,14,Fa younger and healthier man."
OL,16,FThe barrister said the current
OL,17,Fearliest release date from prison for
OL,18,FDunleavy is May 2026 ` before he is
OL,19,Fsentenced for the latest conviction.
