OL,7,FHe added: "We say as part of any
OL,8,Fproper sentencing regime, mercy does
OL,9,Fremain a feature available to the
OL,10,Fcourt."
OL,12,FJudge Lynch said: "It is hard to avoid
OL,13,Fthe comment that your client showed no
OL,14,Fmercy to the victims of this case,
OL,15,Fyour client insisted on them all
OL,16,Fhaving to give evidence, showed no
OL,17,Fmercy even up to this very moment,
OL,18,Fshowed no remorse."
